Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveVeteran Nollywood actor, Richard Mofe-Damijo popularly called RMD, marks his birthday on Wednesday.
Sharing photos on his Instagram page, the actor said “This is 61 and counting! Super grateful and thankful for God’s grace upon my life. Birthdays are a chance to look back and forward and all I see is God’s grace upon the life of this shy Warri boy that said yes to life.”
RMD added, “Grateful for family, staff, friends and business partners and the hands in the creative industry that have given me so much joy and opportunities to shoot my shot! To all July babies, BIG ENERGY all through this perfect month.”
